Just over 2 inches long and made from lightweight PC material, this pint-sized illuminator will fit right in on your key ring as an extra source of light for when you need it most. Despite its compact size, the keylight comes with a respectable 50 Lumen max output, more than enough for up-close illumination, as well as a dimmer, longer lasting Low Mode of just 1 Lumen. In addition to its two modes, the E0 can adjust its brightness infinitely between the 2 designated outputs by holding down its body switch while in Low Mode, allowing for you to choose the perfect brightness level for your situation. The handy light is even USB-rechargeable, leaving no need to keep replacing batteries, saving you time and money.Jetbeam E0 Rechargeable Keychain Light, Assorted Colors
